trans-unit.source: Provides facilities for managing input languages in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 입력된 언어를 관리 하기 위한 기능을 제공 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: Additional languages can be registered by using the Regional and Language Options control panel.
trans-unit.target: 추가 언어 국가 및 언어 옵션 제어판을 사용 하 여 등록할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: From the Languages tab, select "Text Services and input languages", then click the "Details" button to register additional languages.
trans-unit.target: 언어 탭에서 "텍스트 서비스 및 입력된 언어"를 선택 하 고 추가 언어를 등록 하려면 "Details" 단추를 클릭 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The following dialog appears.
![Text services and input languages dialog.](~/add/media/tsf-dialog.PNG "Text services and input languages dialog.")
trans-unit.target: ![텍스트 서비스 및 입력 언어 대화 상자입니다. ] (~/add/media/tsf-dialog.PNG "텍스트 서비스 및 입력 언어 대화 상자.")

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator for currently available input languages.
trans-unit.target: 현재 사용 가능한 입력된 언어에 대 한 열거자를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: An enumerator for currently available input languages, or **null** if no input languages are available.
trans-unit.target: 현재 사용 가능한 입력된 언어에 대 한 열거자 또는 **null** 입력된 언어가 사용 가능한 경우.

trans-unit.source: This property has no default value.
Gets the input language manager associated with the current context.
trans-unit.target: 현재 컨텍스트와 연결 된 입력된 언어 관리자를 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager"></xref> object associated with the current context.
This property has no default value.
Gets or sets the current input language.
trans-unit.target: 현재 입력된 언어를 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object representing the currently selected input language.
This property may not be set to **null**.
The default value is <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture*>.
Raised when an attempt is made to set this property to **null**.
trans-unit.target: 이 속성을 설정 하려고 시도 하면 발생 **null**합니다.

trans-unit.source: Returns the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*> attached property for a specified dependency object.
trans-unit.target: 값을 반환 된 <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*>연결 된 지정된 된 종속성 개체에 대 한 속성.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*>

trans-unit.source: The dependency object for which to retrieve the input language.
A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object representing the input language for the specified dependency object.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>지정된 된 종속성 개체에 대 한 입력된 언어를 나타내는 개체입니다.</xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: Raised when target is **null**.
Returns the value of <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*> attached property for a specified dependency object.
trans-unit.target: 값을 반환 <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*>연결 된 지정된 된 종속성 개체에 대 한 속성.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*>

trans-unit.source: The dependency object for which to retrieve the value of <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*>.
The current value of <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*> for the specified dependency object.
trans-unit.target: 현재 값 <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*>지정된 된 종속성 개체에 대 한.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*>

trans-unit.source: Raised when target is **null**.
Occurs when a change of input language is completed.
trans-unit.target: 입력된 언어의 변경을 완료 될 때 발생 합니다.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
Occurs when a change of input language is initiated.
trans-unit.target: 입력된 언어 변경이 시작 될 때 발생 합니다.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*> attached property.
To be added.
Registers an input language source with the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager"></xref>.
An object that specifies the input language to register.
trans-unit.target: 등록에 입력된 언어를 지정 하는 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: This object must implement the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.IInputLanguageSource"></xref> interface.
Raised when inputLanguageSource is **null**.
Report the completion of a change of input language to the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 입력된 언어를 변경이 완료 되었음을 보고는 <xref href="System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object representing the new input language.
A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object representing the previous input language.
Raised when newLanguageId or previousLanguageId is **null**.
Report the initiation of a change of input language to the <xref href="System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 에 입력 언어 변경 시작 되었음을 보고는 <xref href="System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object representing the new input language.
A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object representing the previous input language.
**true** to indicate that the reported change of input language was accepted; otherwise, **false**.
trans-unit.target: **true 이면** 입력된 언어의 보고 된 변경 허용 되 고, 그렇지 않으면 나타내는 **false**합니다.

trans-unit.source: Raised when newLanguageId or previousLanguageId is **null**.
Identifies the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*> attached property.
To be added.
Sets the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*> attached property on the specified dependency object.
trans-unit.target: 값을 설정 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*>지정 된 종속성 개체에 연결 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*>

trans-unit.source: The dependency object on which to set the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*> attached property.
A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo> object representing the new value for the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*> attached property.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>에 대 한 새 값을 나타내는 개체는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*>연결 된 속성입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.InputLanguage*> </xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>

trans-unit.source: Raised when target is **null**.
Sets the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*> dependency property on the specified dependency object.
trans-unit.target: 값을 설정 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*>종속성 속성에 지정된 된 종속성 개체입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*>

trans-unit.source: The dependency object for which to set the value of <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*>.
A Boolean value to set the <xref:System.Windows.Input.InputLanguageManager.RestoreInputLanguage*> attached property to.
Raised when target is **null**.
